node.text:
Growing up in Chile, Ignacia Riveros knew Moto was her thing from an early age. She’s since proved her skills back home and is coming to America to up her game even further. @rcsxdaytona has been checked off her list and focus now shifts to the Ranch @lorettalynnmx. 

We’re stoked to have @ignaciariveros813 as part of our @foxwomens team! 🎥 @jordanhoov #foxracing @foxracingchile

node.text:
In the words of @caseycochran66, “good vibes” were had in the Sunshine State for @rcsxdaytona. ⁣
⁣
The #foxbrigade took the World Center of Racing by storm with strong finishes on the track and plenty fun off of it. Thanks for having us, @rickycarmichael ✌️ #foxracing 🎥 @jordanhoov

@caseycochran66 @superflytiny24 @kstallings213 @ignaciariveros813 @kenziewatteyne716 @bscheltema115 @shelbs445 @bryceshelly34 @thorpowell15

node.text: We got a chance to check in with Daniel Sanders during his 2 week quarantine upon returning home to Australia after @dakarrally. “Chucky” was able to bring home an impressive 4th place overall finish as a rookie! He’s now out of lockdown and will surely be back ripping at home, so give him a follow to see all of his full throttle antics. @danielsanders_11 #foxracing #dakar

node.text: Name a better escape than that on two wheels. node.text:
Loretta Lynn’s Ranch and the Waverly, Tennessee community have graciously hosted the Fox Amateur Team for decades. Providing our Brand and Riders a platform to showcase their talents and create lasting memories both on and off the track. 

We were devastated to hear of the recent floods that took place and our thoughts are with all of those effected. Fox Racing is proud to support Racers 4 Waverly to help rebuild this special place for all of us.

Click the link in our bio to support the cause and look for a charity Auction coming soon! #foxracing #racers4waverly @road2recovery
